	<section class="article-content clearfix">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="pull-center" src="/lzmk/images/slikeclanci/Enciklopedika2020_web.jpg" alt="" />The Miroslav Krleža Institute of Lexicography</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">is organising the</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE</strong><br /> <strong>ENCYCLOPEDISTICS 2020 – ACHIEVEMENTS AND CHALLENGES</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="/lzmk/enciklopedika-2020" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>MEĐUNARODNI ZNANSTVENI SKUP<br />ENCIKLOPEDIKA 2020 – DOSEZI I IZAZOVI</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>The conference took place on 15 and 16 of October. Due to the current pandemic situation the conference was held at the premises of the institute and online via the Zoom platform.</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">On the occasion of its 70th founding anniversary, the Miroslav Krleža Institute of Lexicography organised the international conference <strong>Encyclopedistics 2020 – Achievements and Challenges,</strong> which was held from 15 to 16 October in Zagreb.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Invited speakers:</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Naja Bentzen</strong>, European Parliament’s Liaison Office in Washington, DC<br /><a href="https://youtu.be/E6spMpBNPIs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Role of Encyclopedias in an Era of Asymmetric Digital Knowledge</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ranko Matasović</strong>, Croatian Academy of Sciences and Arts, Zagreb<br /><a href="https://youtu.be/y8joe5z3mKg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jezična klasifikacija u enciklopedijama / Language Classification in Encyclopedias</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Uri Nodelman</strong>, Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy<br /><a href="https://youtu.be/eW5JyDzo-2I" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i>The Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy</i>: Challenges and Lessons</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Toma Tasovac</strong>, DARIAH-EU, Berlin<br /><a href="https://youtu.be/iQcMZr733dw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Imagining the Future of Dictionaries: Tracing the Early History of e-Lexicography</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Eveline Wandl-Vogt</strong>, Austrian Academy of Sciences, Vienna<br /><a href="https://youtu.be/kBk9hazFh7c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Rethinking a Genre: Accelerating Encylopedic Knowledge into Action on the Example of COVID-19</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The presentations are available <a href="/lzmk/hr/enciklopedika-2020/popis-sudionika" hreflang="hr">here</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Session recordings are available <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLV8WWaI7cuFMG8CXKiL7XqNuUU6FO0Lgr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Papers based on these presentations that are submitted by 1 March 2021 will be published, following the appropriate peer review process, in the lexicography and encyclopedistics journal <a href="http://studialexicographica.lzmk.hr/sl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Studia lexicographica</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Organising Committee:</strong> Ivana Crljenko, Vlatka Dugački, Filip Hameršak, Zdenko Jecić, Nataša Jermen, Iva Klobučar Srbić, Bruno Kragić</p>
<p><strong>Programme Committee:</strong> Petra Bago, Vlaho Bogišić, Damir Boras, Irina Deretić, Peter Jordan, Stipe Kutleša, Janko Lozar, Nives Mikelić Preradović, Željko Pavić, Slaven Ravlić, Krešimir Regan, Hrvoje Stančić, Goran Sunajko, Domagoj Vidović, Antun Vujić</p>
<p><strong>Technical support:</strong> Zdravko Pondelak, Cvijeta Kraus</p>
